{"tid":1655502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人內地住酒店須報告警察","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T06:43:20.000Z","uid":279854,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c244c37b529d8f14445a0d5e1ba45ccf5c524b1f","tid":1655502,"uid":279854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/hong-kong-taiwan-residents-controlled-in-mainland-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fhong-kong-taiwan-residents-controlled-in-mainland-china%2F&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9I429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b00faa8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.bitterwinter.org/hong-kong-taiwan-residents-controlled-in-mainland-china/</a><br />\n為了遏制民主思潮在國內擴散的任何可能性，政府對往返香港、臺灣兩地的遊客採取了嚴格的措施。<br />\n由反對政府強行修訂《逃犯條例》引發的香港民主抗爭運動已經持續近四個月，得到了世界各地的支持。然而中共當局卻將此抗議活動抹黑為「港獨暴動」，並在香港及中國各地採取對策施行打壓，限制進出香港和臺灣，控制涉港信息和出版物。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊客入住酒店須經警察審查</span><br />\n為迎接十一國慶，河南省洛陽市一連鎖酒店的大堂經理通知員工，香港人有內地居住證才可以辦理入住手續，並且必須及時將這些人報告給轄區指定的警官，警官會來酒店盤問香港人來河南旅行的目的。類似措施也針對新疆民眾施行。<br />\n<br />\n對於這一規定，酒店一些員工認為，這是對香港人的歧視。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/%E9%80%9A%E5%B7%9E%E5%8C%BA%E4%B8%80%E6%9D%91%E5%A7%94%E4%BC%9A%E8%B4%B4%E5%87%BA%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6%E2%80%9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%258C%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%259D%2591%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BC%259A%25E8%25B4%25B4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E2%2580%259C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B6%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E4%25B9%25A6%25E2%2580%259D.jpg&h=49448d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>北京通州區一村委會貼出的「安全消防告知書」，禁止對涉港、涉疆、涉藏人員租房</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%A4%E9%87%8C%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%AE%A1%E6%89%B9%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E6%97%85%E6%B8%B8%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E9%2587%258C%25E5%2585%25B3%25E4%25BA%258E%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%25AE%25A1%25E6%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%2597%2585%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5.jpg&h=b6b5446c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>微信群裡關於停止審批個人赴臺旅遊的通知</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/%E6%9F%90%E2%80%9C%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%90%E7%A6%8F%E2%80%9D%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%81%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E6%97%97%E5%B8%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F%25E6%259F%2590%25E2%2580%259C%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B9%2590%25E7%25A6%258F%25E2%2580%259D%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2585%25B3%25E4%25BA%258E%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259E%25B6%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E3%2580%2581%25E5%258F%25B0%25E6%25B9%25BE%25E6%2597%2597%25E5%25B8%259C%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5.jpg&h=68531b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>某家樂福超市關於下架香港、臺灣旗幟的通知</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/20190901-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8-S-CN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.bitterwinter.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F20190901-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258A%25A8-S-CN.jpg&h=d2a3e0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.bitterwinter.org/call-for-papers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3